<s> I agree with Hakon.  </s>
<s> Scalable fonts are the sensible option.  </s>
<s> At the risk of starting a religious flame war, TrueType is the best format on screen because it can be hinted for low resolution.  </s>
<s> So you get the benefits of bit-map and scalable together.  </s>
<s> The font files are big, but there are ways around that.  </s>
